net.consensys.cava.concurrent

Interface CompletableAsyncResult<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the value returned by this result.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AsyncResult<T>

    public interface CompletableAsyncResult<T>
extends AsyncResult<T>
    An AsyncResult that can be later completed successfully with a provided value, or completed with an exception.
